translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: で、昨日あんたママに負けたでしょ？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So, you lost to Mama yesterday, didn't you?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あんたが負けたせいで、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Because you lost,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしが一緒に行動させられてるのよ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm forced to stay with you!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 24時間絶対服従だから！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm under absolute obedience 24 hours a day!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 手を繋いでいるのはママの魔法で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We're holding hands because of Mama's magic,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 手がくっついて外れなくされたからよ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our hands are stuck together and can't be separated!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一緒にアイス食ってんのは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We're eating ice cream together because,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ママに押しつけられたからよ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mama forced me to do it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 他に聞きたいことはある！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Is there anything else you want to know!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ママって呼んでるのは？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Why do you call her Mama?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: へ？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ボッとミックスの顔が赤く染まる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mix's face suddenly flushed red.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そ、れは……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Th-That's...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あんたなんか文句あるの！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Do you have a problem with that!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぶるぶるぶる！　ないです！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: B-b-b-b no, I don't!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 余達はこれから出し物を見に行くつもりだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We plan to go see the performance from now on.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お前らも来るか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Do you guys want to come along?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 呼ぶな！　来るな！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't invite us! Don't come!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ふむ、母と二人きりがいいか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, you want to be alone with your mother, huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言ってない！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I didn't say that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はっはっはっ、他の者がいては、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ha ha ha, having others around

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 母に甘えづらかろうからな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: makes it hard to be spoiled by your mother.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すまないな、皆。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sorry, everyone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今日は遠慮してくれ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Please take a rain check today.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言ってない！　一つも言ってない！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I didn't say that! Not even once!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さ、行くぞ、愛娘よ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well then, let's go, my beloved daughter.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 手を引っ張るなーーー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't pull my hand---!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まあ、祭りを楽しんでるようで何より
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, it’s good to see you enjoying the festival.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 仲良しさんだねぇ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You two get along well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットがぽんやりとした感想を漏らしていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset murmured absentmindedly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達は適当な屋台からいくつか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You picked out some food from a random stall,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 食べ物を見繕い、ベンチに座り朝ご飯にした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: then sat on a bench to have breakfast.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はふはふ、あちあち。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huff huff, hot hot.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: で、情報収集って具体的に何します？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So, what exactly do we do for information gathering?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうだねぇ、はむはむ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well then, hmm hmm...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やっぱりこういうときは専門家に……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After all, in times like this, it’s best to rely on an expert...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おやぁ！　＜エール＞様！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh! Lord <Aile>!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんなとこで会うとは奇遇だねぇ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a coincidence running into you here!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そのとき、どこか下品で暴力的な声が
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At that moment, a vulgar and violent voice

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達にかけられた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: called out to you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケヒヒヒ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kehihihi...
Huh...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: って、あっ！　こいつ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wait, ah! This guy!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おい、＜エール＞、こいつだよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey, <Aile>, it’s this guy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お前の次の対戦相手、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Your next opponent,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物隊長ブロビオって奴！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That monster captain named Brobio!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケヒヒヒ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kehihihi...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 試合を前日に控えてデートたぁ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Going on a date the day before the match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 随分と余裕がおありだねぇ、大将
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you sure seem confident, Captain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いっやぁー、さすがは魔王のお子様！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well now, as expected of the Demon Lord’s child!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 才能がおありなんですなあ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You sure have talent.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺なんて今も必死に修行なくらいなのに！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even I am still desperately training!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なにか秘訣があるんなら是非とも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you have any secrets, I’d love to hear them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あやかりてぇもんですよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I wish to learn from you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ああ、親が強いから強いだけか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, you’re strong only because your parents are strong.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いやー、羨ましいねぇ、大将は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Man, I’m jealous of you, Captain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 嫌味ったらしい口調に、お世辞が見え見えの台詞。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: His tone is sarcastic, and his flattery obvious.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたはブロビオに小馬鹿にされていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were being mocked by Brobio.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すまないな、皆。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sorry, everyone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今日は遠慮してくれ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Please take a rain check today.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言ってない！　一つも言ってない！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I didn't say that! Not even once!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さ、行くぞ、愛娘よ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well then, let's go, my beloved daughter.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 手を引っ張るなーーー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't pull my hand---!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まあ、祭りを楽しんでるようで何より
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, it’s good to see you enjoying the festival.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 仲良しさんだねぇ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You two get along well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットがぽんやりとした感想を漏らしていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset murmured absentmindedly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達は適当な屋台からいくつか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You picked out some food from a random stall,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 食べ物を見繕い、ベンチに座り朝ご飯にした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: then sat on a bench to have breakfast.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はふはふ、あちあち。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huff huff, hot hot.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: で、情報収集って具体的に何します？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So, what exactly do we do for information gathering?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうだねぇ、はむはむ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well then, hmm hmm...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やっぱりこういうときは専門家に……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After all, in times like this, it’s best to rely on an expert...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おやぁ！　＜エール＞様！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh! Lord <Aile>!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんなとこで会うとは奇遇だねぇ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a coincidence running into you here!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そのとき、どこか下品で暴力的な声が
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At that moment, a vulgar and violent voice

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達にかけられた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: called out to you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケヒヒヒ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kehihihi...
Huh...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: って、あっ！　こいつ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wait, ah! This guy!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おい、＜エール＞、こいつだよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey, <Aile>, it’s this guy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お前の次の対戦相手、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Your next opponent,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物隊長ブロビオって奴！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That monster captain named Brobio!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケヒヒヒ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kehihihi...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 試合を前日に控えてデートたぁ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Going on a date the day before the match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 随分と余裕がおありだねぇ、大将
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you sure seem confident, Captain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いっやぁー、さすがは魔王のお子様！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well now, as expected of the Demon Lord’s child!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 才能がおありなんですなあ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You sure have talent.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺なんて今も必死に修行なくらいなのに！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even I am still desperately training!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なにか秘訣があるんなら是非とも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you have any secrets, I’d love to hear them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あやかりてぇもんですよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I wish to learn from you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ああ、親が強いから強いだけか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, you’re strong only because your parents are strong.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いやー、羨ましいねぇ、大将は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Man, I’m jealous of you, Captain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 嫌味ったらしい口調に、お世辞が見え見えの台詞。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: His tone is sarcastic, and his flattery obvious.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたはブロビオに小馬鹿にされていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were being mocked by Brobio.
